author: Rebecca Burn-Callander
title: Made.com raises £38m to expand 'aggressively' in Europe
text: Retail and Consumer Made.com raises £38m to expand 'aggressively' in Europe Following months of speculation, the online furniture business backed by LastMinute.com's Brent Hoberman has revealed its new investors and laid out its growth strategy The Made founders (from left to right): Julien Callede, Chloe Macintosh, Brent Hoberman, Ning Li Photo: Giles Christopher
